---
import LessonShell from '../components/LessonShell.astro';
import VerbWithPreposition from '../components/VerbWithPreposition.jsx';

export const frontmatter = {
  title: "Lektion 2｜動詞與介系詞",
  description: "整理德語動詞與介系詞搭配，練習格位、例句與複習紀錄。",
  category: "文法練習",
  tags: ["B1-B2", "Akkusativ", "Dativ", "系統複習", "學習紀錄"],
  order: 2,
  level: "B1-B2",
  estimatedMinutes: 20,
  theme: "amber"
};
---

<LessonShell frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <VerbWithPreposition client:load />
  </div>

  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>善用已收藏清單：遇到需要反覆整理的動詞，點擊右上角星星，之後可集中複習。</span>
  </li>
  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>聆聽發音：點擊喇叭按鈕聆聽發音，大聲跟讀模仿語調，能加深記憶。</span>
  </li>
  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>注意格位：德文介系詞後面接 Akkusativ 通常有方向、目標性；接 Dativ 多與狀態、位置有關。</span>
  </li>
</LessonShell>
